mal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n所以好人難做真係岩<br />\n有時真係唔好怪人無情"},{"pid":"f705549b9e9c7a8a097940733b83a3ec0d9c2604","tid":376814,"uid":12421,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T10:24:56.000Z","msg":"現實版孤星淚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbc1aad9ac24d852db58fc2d94fe706445ef8b05","tid":376814,"uid":61903,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T11:59:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>現實版孤星淚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n人地偷錢買麵包, 呢條死on9拎去賭<br />\n差幾遠, 真係農夫與蛇個故事囉"},{"pid":"431ac637c0d17a0c10161b8af15e9258e45dbdd4","tid":376814,"uid":35867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T12:01:06.000Z","msg":"on 撚9"},{"pid":"8d50ca16fdf96e7dc3f1448d9b2222fed7841b65","tid":376814,"uid":53223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T12:04:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>裁判官個名</blockquote><br />\n水菜麗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.e123.hk/newsfeed/20131206/_06gg501.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.e123.hk%2Fnewsfeed%2F20131206%2F_06gg501.jpg&h=d052cf35&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n所以咪升唔到，只可以係下級法院做。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd03260f57395d7460eb12f6939d2a0ef46d3667","tid":376814,"uid":110832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T12:06:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">佢去如黃鶴關人乜事咁</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n法官好野，咁都忍到口<br />\n個撚字改乜"},{"pid":"df156cf344bc1fed377531dab2fc0196ff65a1a0","tid":376814,"uid":108238,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score